cc:Work.dc:title: Farmer penguin
cc:Work.dc:description: This little penguin is the twin brother of the gardening penguin. He is more into growing food instead of flowers. He's standing there, proudly, with an ear of grain hanging casually from his little beak. But I think he didn't notice that little caterpillar in his crop... and the spade is grey if you open it with inkscape ?!?
